  "content": "\n \n \n  <h3 data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <section data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n      <section style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n       <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"248\" data-backw=\"578\" data-galleryid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"505088226\" data-ratio=\"0.4287037037037037\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/6cf53346-7be7-4dbb-54e2-b6b0e2454400/public\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/6cf53346-7be7-4dbb-54e2-b6b0e2454400/public\">\n       </section>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section></h3>\n  <h3 style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <section data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n      <section style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n       <section style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n        <hr style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <p style=\"margin: -1.2em 8px 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\"></p>\n        <p style=\"margin: -1.2em 8px 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-family: inherit;font-size: 1em;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:inherit;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 1em;font-family: inherit;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:inherit;\">新智元报道&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong></span></p>\n       </section>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section></h3>\n  <section style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\">编辑：编辑部 HYj</span>\n  </section>\n  <section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <section style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n    <section style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n     <h5 style=\"padding:10px;margin:10px 8px 0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;border-radius:3px;outline:0px;word-spacing:1px !important;max-width:100%;word-break:break-all !important;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">【新智元导读】</strong>Karpathy发出灵魂拷问，评估AI究竟该看哪些指标？答案或许就藏在经典游戏里！最近，加州大学圣迭戈分校Hao AI Lab用超级马里奥等评测AI智能体，Claude 3.7结果令人瞠目结舌。<strong style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\"></strong></span></h5>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 24px 8px;text-indent: 0em;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">LLM评估基准的「黄金标准」，正在失效？</span></p>\n  <section style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-indent: 0em;text-align: justify;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">一大早，AI大神Karpathy发出质疑，「目前存在一种评估危机，我真的不知道现在该看哪些指标了」。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n   <section style=\"width: 100%;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n    <section style=\"width: 100%;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n     <section style=\"overflow: hidden scroll;height: 344px;display: inline-block;color: inherit;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n      <section mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mpa-scroll-mark=\"0\">\n       <p style=\"clear:both;min-height:1em;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"836\" data-backw=\"561\" data-galleryid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"505088223\" data-ratio=\"1.4886104783599088\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8c93d36c-ee18-4d92-18bd-2845ff669e00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"878\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8c93d36c-ee18-4d92-18bd-2845ff669e00/public\"><span style=\"color: inherit;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"></span></p>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(170, 170, 170);margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">上下滑动查看</span></p>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-indent: 0em;text-align: justify;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">诸如MMLU、SWE-Bench Verified、Chatbot Arena等这些基准，各有自己的优劣之处。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-indent: 0em;text-align: justify;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">如果这些都不够，那么游戏算不算？</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-indent: 0em;text-align: justify;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">毕竟，曾经红极一时的AlphaGo是围棋界的头号AI；就连OpenAI也早年涉足游戏领域，拿着自研AI在DOTA国际赛中取得亮眼的成绩。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-indent: 0em;text-align: justify;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">最近，Claude 3.7的出世，让「宝可梦」一时间成为LLM评判的新标杆。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-indent: 0em;text-align: justify;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">UCSD Hao AI Lab再次出手，开源了一种全新的「游戏智能体」，能够实时让计算机使用智能体（CUA）运行解谜、益智等类型的游戏。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin: 24px 8px;\">\n   <iframe class=\"video_iframe rich_pages\" data-vidtype=\"2\" data-mpvid=\"wxv_3881958622770708484\" data-cover=\"http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1nZAibP8Wj79B0HEyDOQTWibGPLpzE2OOAtZh7WzuUiaLMOR5hib5Xw8gLjFaB2piaGAA0xxDfTeBeuPQ%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" data-ratio=\"1.0810810810810811\" data-w=\"640\" data-src=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/readtemplate?t=pages/video_player_tmpl&amp;action=mpvideo&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=wxv_3881958622770708484\"></iframe>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin: 24px 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;text-indent: 0em;\">结果显示，Claude 3.7 Sonnet玩超级马里奥足足撑满90s，直接碾压了OpenAI、Gemini和自家前辈；而GPT-4o一上来就直接挂掉了……</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-indent: 0em;text-align: justify;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">谷歌选手Gemini 1.5 Pro首战即败，而且非常有规律地两步一跳。到了Gemini 2.0虽多走了几步，最终还是栽坑。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-indent: 0em;text-align: justify;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"209\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"461\" data-imgfileid=\"505088161\" data-ratio=\"0.37222222222222223\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b5c950ff-797e-4c9b-50c8-8cf2b471a100/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1239\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b5c950ff-797e-4c9b-50c8-8cf2b471a100/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-indent: 0em;text-align: justify;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">GamingAgent项目代码已开源，下载安装即可观战AI游戏大PK。</span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-indent: 0em;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"285\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"1050\" data-imgfileid=\"505088160\" data-ratio=\"0.5064814814814815\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f4d8dd79-904f-465e-8d9b-83a860526100/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"2074\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f4d8dd79-904f-465e-8d9b-83a860526100/public\"></p>\n  <section style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-indent: 0em;text-align: justify;\">\n   <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 14px;\">开源地址：https://github.com/lmgame-org/GamingAgent</span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><iframe class=\"video_iframe rich_pages\" data-vidtype=\"2\" data-mpvid=\"wxv_3881962181906087944\" data-cover=\"http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1nZAibP8Wj79B0HEyDOQTWibG6v9xFV7Gk7RyYcAWAaeLQA8e7VSiaIsnwkhbCHFzzUQSpT3BCo90qQ%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" data-ratio=\"1.8333333333333333\" data-w=\"1320\" data-src=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/readtemplate?t=pages/video_player_tmpl&amp;action=mpvideo&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=wxv_3881962181906087944\"></iframe><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(143, 149, 158);letter-spacing: 1px;text-indent: 0em;\">「游戏智能体」演示demo</span></p>\n  <section autoid=\"1895\" data-style-type=\"0\" style=\"max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-bottom:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <section style=\"padding: 8px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-left: 6px solid rgb(255, 202, 0);font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: inherit;border-top-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-right-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"></span>GPT-4.5反应迟钝，GPT-4o永远被第一个小怪杀死</p>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;text-indent: 0em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">短短20s，游戏就结束了。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-backh=\"289\" data-backw=\"319\" data-imgfileid=\"505088182\" data-ratio=\"0.9059561128526645\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/74ae65a3-65b0-4724-9f73-d2688f1afd00/public\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"319\" style=\"width: 79%;height: auto !important;flex-basis: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/74ae65a3-65b0-4724-9f73-d2688f1afd00/public\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;text-indent: 0em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;text-indent: 0em;\">相比之下，GPT-4.5的表现就好多了，起码没卡在第一个小怪。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;text-indent: 0em;text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"480\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"548\" data-imgfileid=\"505088163\" data-ratio=\"0.8546875\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/497632ea-4dc2-4e66-2569-3659295eac00/public\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"640\" data-width=\"641\" style=\"width: 79%;height: auto !important;flex-basis: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/497632ea-4dc2-4e66-2569-3659295eac00/public\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;text-indent: 0em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但它的反应还是很迟缓，几乎是两步一停。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;text-indent: 0em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">跳过一个矮水管之前，也要犹豫片刻，感觉像是刚学会了游戏操作，还在蹒跚学步。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-backh=\"480\" data-backw=\"562\" data-imgfileid=\"505088184\" data-ratio=\"0.8546875\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/0655bc46-58d5-4cf2-9798-432357eff400/public\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"640\" style=\"width: 79%;height: auto !important;flex-basis: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/0655bc46-58d5-4cf2-9798-432357eff400/public\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;text-indent: 0em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">一个稍高点的水管，尝试了7次，足足花了10s才跳了过去。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-backh=\"480\" data-backw=\"562\" data-imgfileid=\"505088185\" data-ratio=\"0.8549141965678627\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f24934af-6d31-4942-2099-03ee25f3b800/public\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"641\" style=\"width: 79%;height: auto !important;flex-basis: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f24934af-6d31-4942-2099-03ee25f3b800/public\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;text-indent: 0em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">好不容易跳了过去，就撞到小怪死掉了。第一回合就这样告终了。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-backh=\"480\" data-backw=\"562\" data-imgfileid=\"505088186\" data-ratio=\"0.8549141965678627\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a52c20d0-aba1-44b0-67fc-9337d4b10a00/public\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"641\" style=\"width: 78%;height: auto !important;flex-basis: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a52c20d0-aba1-44b0-67fc-9337d4b10a00/public\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;text-indent: 0em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">更好笑的是，第二回合的时候，GPT-4.5又栽倒在了第一个小怪那里。毕竟和GPT-4o同属于OpenAI家族，操作都比较菜<span style=\"font-size: 15px;text-decoration: line-through;\">（bushi）</span>。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-backh=\"480\" data-backw=\"562\" data-imgfileid=\"505088187\" data-ratio=\"0.8549141965678627\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e041209d-6acf-4e0a-58bb-77e9e6fec200/public\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"641\" style=\"width: 79%;height: auto !important;flex-basis: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e041209d-6acf-4e0a-58bb-77e9e6fec200/public\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;text-indent: 0em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">第三回合表现也比较一般，还不如第一回合。第一个矮水管就卡了半天，搁水管底下卡了快10s才想起来跳。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-backh=\"480\" data-backw=\"562\" data-imgfileid=\"505088188\" data-ratio=\"0.8549141965678627\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e45008c1-35e6-46ca-f411-822db4485800/public\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"641\" style=\"width: 79%;height: auto !important;flex-basis: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e45008c1-35e6-46ca-f411-822db4485800/public\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;text-indent: 0em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">最后虽然丝滑地跳过了第二个水管，但还是被小怪杀死了，还没有第一回合走得远。第一回合起码跳过了第三个水管，虽说刚跳过就被杀了。</span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin: 24px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-backh=\"480\" data-backw=\"562\" data-imgfileid=\"505088189\" data-ratio=\"0.8549141965678627\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/7b2a1d07-89d8-4e4e-d683-9926491da800/public\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"641\" style=\"width: 79%;height: auto !important;flex-basis: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/7b2a1d07-89d8-4e4e-d683-9926491da800/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 24px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><iframe class=\"video_iframe rich_pages\" data-vidtype=\"2\" data-mpvid=\"wxv_3881960983056613377\" data-cover=\"http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1nZAibP8Wj79B0HEyDOQTWib7wLt4s0PGcmIOq7DyJO3fttSUiaRql561v4MqXmib9WjLZPGJ9nFszCg%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" data-ratio=\"1.1685185185185185\" data-w=\"1262\" data-src=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/readtemplate?t=pages/video_player_tmpl&amp;action=mpvideo&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=wxv_3881960983056613377\"></iframe><span style=\"color: rgb(143, 149, 158);letter-spacing: 1px;text-indent: 0em;font-size: 14px;\">GPT-4.5完整视频</span></p>\n  <section autoid=\"1895\" data-style-type=\"0\" style=\"max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-bottom:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <section style=\"padding: 8px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-left: 6px solid rgb(255, 202, 0);font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: inherit;border-top-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-right-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"></span>Gemini 1.5两步一跳，2.0栽进坑里</p>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <h2 style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 24px 8px;text-indent: 0em;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;text-indent: 0em;\">到了谷歌这边，Gemini 1.5 Pro首战也不如意，没能逃过第一个小怪的魔爪。</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;text-indent: 0em;text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"290\" data-backw=\"319\" data-height=\"290\" data-imgfileid=\"505088165\" data-ratio=\"0.9090909090909091\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1699fc15-2ce5-4c7d-7fd0-bc2c3ea17200/public\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"319\" data-width=\"319\" style=\"width: 79%;height: auto !important;flex-basis: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1699fc15-2ce5-4c7d-7fd0-bc2c3ea17200/public\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;text-indent: 0em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">第二回合Gemini 1.5算是躲过了第一个小怪，甚至还碰到了问号箱，吃到了蘑菇。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;text-indent: 0em;text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"291\" data-backw=\"319\" data-height=\"291\" data-imgfileid=\"505088166\" data-ratio=\"0.9122257053291536\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b2ae1ed4-28a2-4951-9667-f2f0b4d4be00/public\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"319\" data-width=\"319\" style=\"width: 79%;height: auto !important;flex-basis: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b2ae1ed4-28a2-4951-9667-f2f0b4d4be00/public\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;text-indent: 0em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">有趣的是，和GPT-4.5两步一停不同，Gemini 1.5是「两步一跳」。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;text-indent: 0em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">走了这么一小段路，一共就跳了9回。地板上也跳一跳，水管上也跳一跳。</span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-backh=\"259\" data-backw=\"284\" data-imgfileid=\"505088218\" data-ratio=\"0.9119718309859155\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/03965cd4-98f5-43ab-016f-b9e5e62ef200/public\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"284\" style=\"width: 79%;height: auto !important;flex-basis: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/03965cd4-98f5-43ab-016f-b9e5e62ef200/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;text-indent: 0em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">最后也是跳过了第三根水管，甚至差点跳过了第四个，算是走得比GPT-4.5要远。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"291\" data-backw=\"319\" data-height=\"291\" data-imgfileid=\"505088190\" data-ratio=\"0.9122257053291536\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/03f4dfdc-1017-4d02-0c98-99fce1beb100/public\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"319\" data-width=\"319\" style=\"width: 79%;height: auto !important;flex-basis: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/03f4dfdc-1017-4d02-0c98-99fce1beb100/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;text-indent: 0em;\">至于更新的Gemini 2.0 Flash，表现上不出意外地要好得多。</span><span data-lark-record-format=\"docx/record\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;text-indent: 0em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">首先，跳得更大胆；其次，跳得也更流畅。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;text-indent: 0em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">跳到了「前人」未曾涉足的更高的平台上，而且10s就轻松跳过了前面三个水管。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-backh=\"407\" data-backw=\"480\" data-imgfileid=\"505088191\" data-ratio=\"0.8479166666666667\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e53c3132-cd2d-4dc8-110f-d9bd54b76300/public\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"480\" style=\"width: 79%;height: auto !important;flex-basis: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e53c3132-cd2d-4dc8-110f-d9bd54b76300/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;text-indent: 0em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">虽然第二回合的时候也惨遭第一个小怪的毒手。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;text-indent: 0em;text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"477\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"544\" data-imgfileid=\"505088168\" data-ratio=\"0.8486739469578783\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/91321b9a-5e40-4e5c-57fa-c0c4f0e18700/public\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"641\" data-width=\"641\" style=\"width: 79%;height: auto !important;flex-basis: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/91321b9a-5e40-4e5c-57fa-c0c4f0e18700/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;text-indent: 0em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但最后走得比OpenAI家族和Gemini 1.5都远——跳过了第四根水管，栽倒在了一个没能跳过去的坑中。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-backh=\"491\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"505088193\" data-ratio=\"0.8486739469578783\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/39ac4445-5d89-4410-c048-d04a14c25d00/public\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"641\" style=\"width: 79%;height: auto !important;flex-basis: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/39ac4445-5d89-4410-c048-d04a14c25d00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe class=\"video_iframe rich_pages\" data-vidtype=\"2\" data-mpvid=\"wxv_3881959728238460940\" data-cover=\"http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1nZAibP8Wj79B0HEyDOQTWibJ9qpddicZlYlSAQQsgdMgCNwD5icVbfOHAPDYAZBOBD14iaJX9gfcWofw%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" data-ratio=\"1.1777777777777778\" data-w=\"848\" data-src=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/readtemplate?t=pages/video_player_tmpl&amp;action=mpvideo&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=wxv_3881959728238460940\"></iframe><span style=\"text-align: center;letter-spacing: 1px;text-indent: 0em;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">Gemini 2.0 Flash完整视频</span><span data-lark-record-format=\"docx/record\"></span></p>\n  <section autoid=\"1895\" data-style-type=\"0\" style=\"max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-bottom:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <section style=\"padding: 8px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-left: 6px solid rgb(255, 202, 0);font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: inherit;border-top-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-right-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"></span>Claude 3.7 Sonnet发现隐藏奖励</p>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <h2 style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 24px 8px;text-indent: 0em;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;text-indent: 0em;\">相比之下，Anthropic的Claude，就要惊艳多了。</span></h2>\n  <section style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-indent: 0em;text-align: justify;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"339\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"521\" data-imgfileid=\"505088167\" data-ratio=\"0.6030092592592593\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/959b537b-3c0c-4f8d-f72c-82056e442900/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"864\" data-width=\"864\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/959b537b-3c0c-4f8d-f72c-82056e442900/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-indent: 0em;text-align: justify;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">相比于Gemini两步一跳的操作，Claude 3.7的操作更加丝滑，走得也远很多。</span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;text-indent: 0em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">尤其是在跳跃的时机上，显得更有章法，碰到水管、碰到坑才会跳。</span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-backh=\"266\" data-backw=\"288\" data-imgfileid=\"505088219\" data-ratio=\"0.9236111111111112\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/6f87ebbb-e51a-4806-d180-c26a3de4db00/public\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"288\" style=\"width: 79%;height: auto !important;flex-basis: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/6f87ebbb-e51a-4806-d180-c26a3de4db00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;text-indent: 0em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">此外，还会有意识地通过跳跃来躲避小怪。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;text-indent: 0em;text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"299\" data-backw=\"324\" data-height=\"299\" data-imgfileid=\"505088170\" data-ratio=\"0.9228395061728395\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/12b748cd-5467-4f52-8f49-8f6de3e22500/public\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"324\" data-width=\"324\" style=\"width: 79%;height: auto !important;flex-basis: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/12b748cd-5467-4f52-8f49-8f6de3e22500/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;text-indent: 0em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">跳过了Gemini 2.0 Flash两回合都没跳过去的坑，Claude操作下的马里奥终于是吃到了金币；终于是碰到了除了哥布林（形似蘑菇）之外的小怪——库巴（形似乌龟）；甚至还碰出了隐藏奖励——超级星星。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;text-indent: 0em;text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"299\" data-backw=\"324\" data-height=\"299\" data-imgfileid=\"505088171\" data-ratio=\"0.9228395061728395\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/0b1be68d-ddbe-46c7-5192-248a3a68f900/public\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"324\" data-width=\"324\" style=\"width: 79%;height: auto !important;flex-basis: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/0b1be68d-ddbe-46c7-5192-248a3a68f900/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;text-indent: 0em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">最后是掉到了阶梯平台之间的坑里，结束了游戏。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;text-indent: 0em;text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"299\" data-backw=\"324\" data-height=\"299\" data-imgfileid=\"505088169\" data-ratio=\"0.9228395061728395\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/dedc1c07-85b2-4a19-9ac8-9904e6994f00/public\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"324\" data-width=\"324\" style=\"width: 79%;height: auto !important;flex-basis: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/dedc1c07-85b2-4a19-9ac8-9904e6994f00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section autoid=\"1895\" data-style-type=\"0\" style=\"max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-bottom:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <section style=\"padding: 8px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-left: 6px solid rgb(255, 202, 0);font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: inherit;border-top-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-right-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"></span>AI大战2048益智游戏，GPT-4o拿不出手</p>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <h2 style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 24px 8px;text-indent: 0em;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;text-indent: 0em;\">接下来，再看一个益智类的游戏2048。</span></h2>\n  <section style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-indent: 0em;text-align: justify;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">可能很多人对这款游戏并不熟悉，规则是通过滑动进行拼图，玩家将带有相同数字的方块合并，达到可能最高的数值。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-indent: 0em;text-align: justify;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">GPT-4o在挑战过程中，因为思考过久，陷入困境。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-indent: 0em;text-align: justify;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">而Claude 3.7虽多走了几步，比GPT-4o强不少，但最终还是以失败告终。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"309\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"352\" data-imgfileid=\"505088177\" data-ratio=\"0.55\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/bb8da9c2-2ad6-4ede-1233-921e5957b600/public\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"640\" data-width=\"640\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/bb8da9c2-2ad6-4ede-1233-921e5957b600/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section autoid=\"1895\" data-style-type=\"0\" style=\"max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-bottom:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <section style=\"padding: 8px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-left: 6px solid rgb(255, 202, 0);font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: inherit;border-top-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-right-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"></span>俄罗斯方块，智商在线</p>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 24px 8px;text-indent: 0em;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">那么Claude 3.7玩俄罗斯方块的表现，又如何呢？</span><span style=\"font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-backh=\"477\" data-backw=\"480\" data-imgfileid=\"505088178\" data-ratio=\"0.99375\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f4594c3d-566b-4717-c037-b287b0ed4000/public\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"480\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f4594c3d-566b-4717-c037-b287b0ed4000/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-indent: 0em;text-align: justify;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Anthropic开发者关系负责人Alex Albert称赞道，「非常酷！我们需要把每一款电子游戏都变成一种评估工具」。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-indent: 0em;text-align: justify;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"116\" data-imgfileid=\"505088172\" data-ratio=\"0.09259259259259259\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/6d5fd552-49f0-408a-4834-43464919f000/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1248\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/6d5fd552-49f0-408a-4834-43464919f000/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-indent: 0em;text-align: justify;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">已经有网友在评论区许愿，让Grok 3加入战场。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-indent: 0em;text-align: justify;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">看来，LLM评估即将开辟一条全新的路。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;line-height:1.75em;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\">参考资料：</span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;line-height:1.75em;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\">https://x.com/haoailab/status/1895557913621795076</span></p>\n  <p style=\"white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;line-height:1.75em;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\">https://x.com/haoailab/status/1895605453461340472</span></p>\n  <p style=\"white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;line-height:1.75em;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\">https://lmgame.org/#/aboutus</span></p>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n \n",
